About 11 people were confirmed dead, while seven were injured in a multiple accident that resulted in fire outbreak at Isaara Bridge, Ogere on the Lagos-Ibadan Expressway on Saturday night.
 
Sector Commander, Federal Road Safety Corps (FRSC) in Ogun State, Mr. Ahmed Umar, who confirmed the incident to newsmen in Abeokuta yesterday, said the incident happened on Saturday night.
 
Umar noted that the accident, which occurred at 10:35p.m.was caused by excessive speed and dangerous driving, saying it involved two Mazda buses and a car. 